# App Router / UI

- Default to Server Components; add `"use client"` only when needed.
- Reuse `src/lib/supabase/server.ts` or `client.ts` — do not invent new Supabase client factories.
- After UI edits, follow `.cursor/skills/verify-frontend-change/SKILL.md` before calling the work done.
- For landing/visual work, also follow `.cursor/skills/ui-design/SKILL.md`.
